nodes.text: Vanguard Five was a pilot callsign of the New Republic's Vanguard Squadron. When a new pilot was added to the squadron after Lindon Javes was given command, the pilot was given the callsign Vanguard Five.

Vanguard Five is the callsign of the New Republic player character in the 2020 video game Star Wars: Squadrons. As the player names are customizable, other characters refer to the pilot solely as "Vanguard Five".
